'Buffet was hilarious. I had one plate each with my wife, and they decided to charge us additional rate because.. get this. "We ate too much" Wife and I are under 150 pounds and we couldnt understand this. However, you will learn that this place is the capital of Nickel and Diming. You get 2 free water bottles in your room. They tell you additional are 5 bucks a pop. If you ask about the tap water, they tell you NOT to drink it. The beds are the worst I have ever slept on. Did they also tell you there is a federali training center behind the hotel?'